From: Oleksandr Natalenko <oleksandr@natalenko.name>
Subject: [pf-curated-6.4] fixes: miscellaneous fixes

Re-cut from natalenko's pf-kernel branch fixes-6.4 (tip 472bae48c76f)
as a single bulk diff, restricted to the files this overlay's curation
kept on the 6.4 slot. Source: codeberg.org/pf-kernel/linux.

